title: Oceanic LOL Cup - Have you registered yet?

embed.description: Hey guys and girls! Why not grab you and 4 mates and enter the Oceanic LOL Cup! Entry is the $25 per team and you could win $500 RP! Here's what you need to know :D. Details - The Oceanic LoL Cup is a competition being hosted by Oceanic LoL on Facebook.

body:
For only $25 a team (working out to $1 per person per game!) you can get your chance to compete for $500 RP!
Each team get's a minimum of 5 B01 games, so there's lot's of chances for your team to pick up some wins

Why not get some mates and get registered today!

7 teams registered so far, 17 positions open!
Registration closes 30th of April!
Send your information to: Oceaniclolcup@gmail.com
